<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٥٦٤ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2711">‌سُوَيْدٌ </a>قَالَ: أَنْبَأَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3875">‌عَبْدُ اللهِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2332">‌سَعِيدِ بْنِ أَبِي عَرُوبَةَ </a>قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">‌قَتَادَةُ </a>: «كَانَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">‌أَنَسٌ </a>يَأْمُرُ بِالتَّذْنُوبِ فَيُقْرَضُ».<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>